screen_desc:
A screenshot of a mobile app interface showing various account management options. The top of the screen displays the time (10:24) and battery status (100%). Below that is a search bar with options to search or ask a question, and icons for scanning and voice input. The list of options includes:

- Switch Accounts
- Your Addresses
- Manage saved IDs
- Manage Your Amazon Family
- Manage your Profiles
- 1-Click settings
- Manage Prime Membership
- Content Library
- Devices
- Manage your Household
- Manage Digital Delivery
- Teens Program
- Audible settings

At the bottom, there are navigation icons for Home, Profile, Cart, Menu, and Notifications.
